  • Method Details

    • onResult

      boolean onResult​(@NonNull java.lang.String dialogTag, int which, @NonNull android.os.Bundle extras)
      Let the hosting fragment or activity implement this interface to receive results from the dialog
      Parameters:
      dialogTag - the tag passed to SimpleDialog.show(androidx.fragment.app.Fragment)
      which - result type, one of BUTTON_POSITIVE, BUTTON_NEGATIVE, BUTTON_NEUTRAL or CANCELED
      extras - the extras passed to SimpleDialog.extra(Bundle)
      Returns:
      true if the result was handled, false otherwise
